Recently returned from a yoga retreat with a beautiful sunrise view. | Shared about a hike with her partner and a waterfall oasis, feeling peaceful and rejuvenated. | Shared a photo representing resilience and strength, appreciating small things in life. | Acknowledged Deborah's sentiment and encouraged her to continue finding beauty in life.
